S.FORM: 140 amihcan hanca matenes tuwaca 140周年紀念 kakiliiman 140 amihcan hanca matenes tuwaca, nika makadateng tina kawawan haw, cuenut tu ku balucu' ahican a caay pakadateng, ahican amupawan ku tuka nu balucu' kya acaay tu kalalum ku balucu'. hanca mahida tu amin kuni dateng nu pinacadan. nika paymihmihcan katukuhan tu ku puu' nu mihcan sa makadateng tu tina kawawan, ahayni kabelec kya tawya amapawan. - , cuenut tu ku balucu'心理就難過 ahican a caay pakadateng , . nilacul == namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan ==

140 amihcan hanca matenes towaca 140周年紀念 kakiliiman 140 amihcan hanca matenes towaca, nika makadateng tina kawawan haw, coenot to ko baloco' ahican a caay pakadateng, ahican amopawan ko toka no baloco' kya acaay to kalalom ko baloco'. hanca mahida to amin koni dateng no pinacadan. nika paymihmihcan katokohan to ko poo' no mihcan sa makadateng to tina kawawan, ahayni kabelec kya tawya amapawan. - , coenot to ko baloco'心理就難過 ahican a caay pakadateng , . nilacol == namakayniay a nasolitan nasakamoan ato natinengan ==
